      <title>美国糖产量创历史新高，糖果制造商可稍事休息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/candymakers-catch-a-breather-as-us-set-for-record-sugar-output</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在去年支付了创纪录的糖价后，美国糖果制造商现在可以松一口气了：随着国内产量即将攀升至历史最高水平，成本正在下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/candymakers-catch-a-breather-as-us-set-for-record-sugar-output</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 12:47:17 GMT</pubDate>
